  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.7">
<l>nīrilē niṉṟayark kiṉṟōm nītiyal lātaṉa ceytāy</l>
<l>ūrakañ cālavuñ cēyttā lūḻiyel lāmuṇar vāṉē</l>
<l>ārva muṉakkē yuṭaiyō mammaṉai mārkāṇi loṭṭār</l>
<l>pōra viṭāyeṅkaḷ paṭṭaip pūṅkurun tēṟiyi rātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We are becoming weary by standing in the water. You do unfair things!</l>
<l>The village and the houses are very far, oh! O You who are awake</l>
<l rend="indent">during [the end of] the aeons!</l>
<l>It is for You that we bear affection. If [our] mothers see [this], they will not allow [us home].</l>
<l>Do not remain atop the flowering sweet lime tree, let go of our silk clothes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
